{"thag14.2:0.1":"Theragatha 14.2 ","thag14.2:0.2":"Cuddasakanipata ","thag14.2:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag14.2:0.4":"Godattattheragatha ","thag14.2:1.1":"“Yathapi bhaddo ajanno, ","thag14.2:1.2":"dhure yutto dhurassaho; ","thag14.2:1.3":"Mathito atibharena, ","thag14.2:1.4":"samyugam nativattati. ","thag14.2:2.1":"Evam pannaya ye titta, ","thag14.2:2.2":"samuddo varina yatha; ","thag14.2:2.3":"Na pare atimannanti, ","thag14.2:2.4":"ariyadhammova paninam. ","thag14.2:3.1":"Kale kalavasam patta, ","thag14.2:3.2":"bhavabhavavasam gata; ","thag14.2:3.3":"Nara dukkham nigacchanti, ","thag14.2:3.4":"tedha socanti manava. ","thag14.2:4.1":"Unnata sukhadhammena, ","thag14.2:4.2":"dukkhadhammena conata; ","thag14.2:4.3":"Dvayena bala hannanti, ","thag14.2:4.4":"yathabhutam adassino. ","thag14.2:5.1":"Ye ca dukkhe sukhasminca, ","thag14.2:5.2":"majjhe sibbinimaccagu; ","thag14.2:5.3":"Thita te indakhilova, ","thag14.2:5.4":"na te unnataonata. ","thag14.2:6.1":"Na heva labhe nalabhe, ","thag14.2:6.2":"na yase na ca kittiya; ","thag14.2:6.3":"Na nindayam pasamsaya, ","thag14.2:6.4":"na te dukkhe sukhamhi ca. ","thag14.2:7.1":"Sabbattha te na limpanti, ","thag14.2:7.2":"udabinduva pokkhare; ","thag14.2:7.3":"Sabbattha sukhita dhira, ","thag14.2:7.4":"sabbattha aparajita. ","thag14.2:8.1":"Dhammena ca alabho yo, ","thag14.2:8.2":"yo ca labho adhammiko; ","thag14.2:8.3":"Alabho dhammiko seyyo, ","thag14.2:8.4":"yance labho adhammiko. ","thag14.2:9.1":"Yaso ca appabuddhinam, ","thag14.2:9.2":"vinnunam ayaso ca yo; ","thag14.2:9.3":"Ayasova seyyo vinnunam, ","thag14.2:9.4":"na yaso appabuddhinam. ","thag14.2:10.1":"Dummedhehi pasamsa ca, ","thag14.2:10.2":"vinnuhi garaha ca ya; ","thag14.2:10.3":"Garahava seyyo vinnuhi, ","thag14.2:10.4":"yance balappasamsana. ","thag14.2:11.1":"Sukhanca kamamayikam, ","thag14.2:11.2":"dukkhanca pavivekiyam; ","thag14.2:11.3":"Pavivekadukkham seyyo, ","thag14.2:11.4":"yance kamamayam sukham. ","thag14.2:12.1":"Jivitanca adhammena, ","thag14.2:12.2":"dhammena marananca yam; ","thag14.2:12.3":"Maranam dhammikam seyyo, ","thag14.2:12.4":"yance jive adhammikam. ","thag14.2:13.1":"Kamakopappahina ye, ","thag14.2:13.2":"santacitta bhavabhave; ","thag14.2:13.3":"Caranti loke asita, ","thag14.2:13.4":"natthi tesam piyapiyam. ","thag14.2:14.1":"Bhavayitvana bojjhange, ","thag14.2:14.2":"indriyani balani ca; ","thag14.2:14.3":"Pappuyya paramam santim, ","thag14.2:14.4":"parinibbantinasava”ti. ","thag14.2:14.5":"… Godatto thero … ","thag14.2:14.6":"Cuddasakanipato nitthito. ","thag14.2:15.0":"Tatruddanam ","thag14.2:15.1":"Revato ceva godatto, ","thag14.2:15.2":"thera dve te mahiddhika; ","thag14.2:15.3":"Cuddasamhi nipatamhi, ","thag14.2:15.4":"gathayo atthavisatiti. "}